author: ekoneil
msg: Fixup the support for Struts 1.1 / 1.2 in the NetUI's build files.
- add a "struts.version" property which can be passed when creating a web application.  Valid values are "1.1" and "1.2", with the latter as the default.
- fixup the coreWeb build.xml file to remove the overwrite of 1.2 with 1.1
- switch to using <fileset>s for the Struts 1.1 / 1.2 WEB-INF and WEB-INF/lib resources
- same thing for the NetUI runtime
